short.zh_CN: 将图像保存为PDF、JPG、PNG或WebP。使用图像上下文菜单。将图像保存为PDF、JPG、PNG或WebP。

long.am,ar,de,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,en_US,es,es_4: This extension enables users to save images from web pages in various formats such as PDF, JPG, PNG, and WEBP. It provides a seamless and efficient way to download and store images in the desired format directly from the browser.
long.bg,bn,ca,cs,da,te:
Funcs:
1. Enables saving images from web pages.
2. Supports multiple image formats including PDF, JPG, PNG, and WEBP.
3. Provides seamless integration with web browsers.
4. Allows users to download images in their desired format.
5. Offers efficiency in image downloading process.
6. Streamlines the image saving process.
7. Works directly within the browser interface.
8. Enhances user convenience in managing images.
9. Facilitates quick access to saved images.
10. Enables organizing images by format.
11. Offers flexibility in choosing image file types.
12. Supports batch downloading of images.
13. Ensures compatibility with various web browsers.
14. Provides options for customizing image download settings.
15. Enables users to save images with customizable filenames.
16. Offers a user-friendly interface for easy navigation.
17. Enhances productivity by simplifying image saving tasks.
18. Allows users to quickly switch between different image formats.
19. Provides reliable image saving functionality.
20. Integrates smoothly with existing browser workflows.
